<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Neon Injector"
  description="Review the terms and conditions for using Neon Injector, outlining user responsibilities, usage guidelines, and liability terms."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-8 text-center">Terms of Service</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="mb-6">Welcome to Neon Injector. By using our tool or accessing our website, you agree to comply with the following Terms of Service. These terms govern your use of Neon Injector for Mobile Legends skin customization and outline your responsibilities as a user. Please read them carefully.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">1. Usage Guidelines</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">To ensure a safe and fair experience for all users, you must adhere to the following guidelines when using Neon Injector:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Age Requirement</strong>: You must be at least 13 years old to use Neon Injector, in compliance with applicable laws.</li>
            <li><strong>Personal Use Only</strong>: Neon Injector is intended for personal, non-commercial use. Do not use it for profit or unauthorized distribution.</li>
            <li><strong>Compliance with Game Rules</strong>: Do not use Neon Injector to engage in activities that violate Mobile Legends’ Terms of Service, such as altering gameplay mechanics.</li>
            <li><strong>No Reverse Engineering</strong>: Do not attempt to reverse-engineer, modify, or redistribute Neon Injector’s code or assets.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">2. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">As a user of Neon Injector, you are responsible for your actions and the consequences of using our tool. Key responsibilities include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Accepting Risks</strong>: You acknowledge and accept all risks associated with using Neon Injector, including potential account bans or data loss by Mobile Legends or Moonton.</li>
            <li><strong>No Unauthorized Distribution</strong>: Do not share modified or unofficial versions of Neon Injector, as this may harm other users or the tool’s reputation.</li>
            <li><strong>Reporting Issues</strong>: Promptly report any bugs, errors, or security concerns to our support team via the <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> or at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3. Liability</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Neon Injector is provided “as is” without warranties of any kind, express or implied. The Neon Injector team is not liable for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Damages or Losses</strong>: Any damages, losses, or disruptions caused by the use of Neon Injector, including data loss or device issues.</li>
            <li><strong>Account Penalties</strong>: Account suspensions, bans, or other penalties imposed by Moonton or Mobile Legends due to third-party tool usage.</li>
            <li><strong>Service Interruptions</strong>: Any interruptions, errors, or unavailability of Neon Injector’s functionality.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">4. Termination</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">We reserve the right to suspend or terminate access to Neon Injector for users who violate these Terms of Service, engage in harmful activities, or misuse the tool in ways that affect other users or our reputation. If your access is terminated, you may contact us via the <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> for clarification.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">If you have questions about these Terms of Service or need assistance, please reach out to our support team via the <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> or email us at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a>. We’re here to help you use Neon Injector responsibly.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>